ges_of_South_America\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FIndigenous_languages_of_South_America&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=5fd93278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indigenous_languages_of_South_America</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ethnologue.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ethnologue.com%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=36b3e278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ethnologue.com/</a> 以前免費 而家有某程度嘅paywall<br />\n<br />\nRevitalization唔係冇人做<br />\n<a href=\"https://latinamericanpost.com/29301-latin-american-indigenous-people-fight-for-the-survival-of-their-languages\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flatinamericanpost.com%2F29301-latin-american-indigenous-people-fight-for-the-survival-of-their-languages&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=b151385b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://latinamericanpost.com/29301-latin-american-indigenous-people-fight-for-the-survival-of-their-languages</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"其實睇落去幾多下喎"},{"pid":"d03b83259c0c1fe270e638c6c881ed21e291a302","tid":2202873,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://neomexicanismos.com/cultura-mexico/dia-del-padre-como-se-dice-papa-en-nahuatl-lenguas-indigenas-mexico/?fbclid=IwAR0kXQJsPomKqn50mqb1QaR5gE90Jhx6KYwfVZdO7JRsfgpAX8naOh0ROCU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fneomexicanismos.com%2Fcultura-mexico%2Fdia-del-padre-como-se-dice-papa-en-nahuatl-lenguas-indigenas-mexico%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0kXQJsPomKqn50mqb1QaR5gE90Jhx6KYwfVZdO7JRsfgpAX8naOh0ROCU&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=b37da9f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://neomexicanismos.com/cultura-mexico/dia-del-padre-como-se-dice-papa-en-nahuatl-lenguas-indigenas-mexico/?fbclid=IwAR0kXQJsPomKqn50mqb1QaR5gE90Jhx6KYwfVZdO7JRsfgpAX8naOh0ROCU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥仲係北美洲，有部分喺中美咁解<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥都有成68種原住民語言，標題係用原住民語講父親節快樂"}]}